{
  "id": "f13v",
  "recto_verso": "verso",
  "gathering_position": 13,
  "damage": null,
  "hand_notes": "final lines of main text; hand notably calm here relative to earlier passages",
  "section_breaks": [],
  "vellum_stock": "standard",
  "lines": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Das hat mich getröstet, als ich es endlich gefaßt habe.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Ich bin nit das letzte glied. Ich bin eines von vielen.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "Das ist nit eine kleine ehre, es ist die richtige ehre:",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "die ehre des gliedes, das in der kette hängt vnd die kette",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "nicht zerreißt. Ich halte. Das iß genug.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "Ich schließe jetzt den ersten teil dises buches vnd ich",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "weiß nit, ob ich es je gelesen haben werde. Vielleicht",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "werde ich es verbrennen. Vielleicht werde ichs verwahren.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "Vielleicht wird es jemand finden nach meinem tod vnd",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "fragen: wer war Konrad, der das geschrieben hat? Vnd",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "die antwort ist: er war ein schreiber, ein kleiner schreiber,",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "der dreißig jar lang das wort durch sich durchgelassen hat",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "vnd dabei gelernt hat, was er nit anders hätte lernen können.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Das ist die ganze geschichte. Das ist das bekenntnis.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Es ist nit so groß wie Augustinus. Aber es ist meins.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Vnd das meins-sein ist das einzige, das ich Gott geben",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "kann, der schon alles hat. Also gebe ich es ihm. Hiermit.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "In diser stund. In disem jar MCCCCLVII. Gott sey lob.",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Vnd noch eins will ich sagen, am ende dises ersten teils:",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "das schreiben hat mich nit klug gemacht. Es hat mich stiller",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "gemacht. Vnd die stille ist vielleicht das anfangsstück",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "der weisheit. Ich will mich damit zufrieden geben.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    }
  ]
}
